                        <interp inst="t18640201-name-154" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18640201-name-154" type="given" value="JOHN HARRISON"></interp>JOHN HARRISON SMITH</persName>
                  </hi>. My private residence is at 49, Inverness-terrace, Bayswaterâ€”I managed the vessel while she was hereâ€”I know the owner Mr. William Weemys Kerr, perfectly wellâ€”his office is in Londonâ€”he is a Scotchman.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. RIBTON</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> How long have you known him? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Twenty or twenty-five yearsâ€”I believe he was born in Scotlandâ€”I am quite certain he was not born in New Yorkâ€”I have heard him say he was born in Scotland, and I have heard so from his relatives.</p>
